{
  "info": {
    "name": "CRM 4.0 - Event-Driven Architecture",
    "description": "Coleção completa para testar a arquitetura 4.0 com Event-Driven, Workers, Idempotência e Estados de Processamento",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "version": "2.0.0"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "📅 Appointment (Event-Driven)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Particular",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Correlation-Id",
                "value": "{{$guid}}",
                "description": "Rastreamento distribuído"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Idempotency-Key",
                "value": "{{patientId}}_create_{{$timestamp}}",
                "description": "Idempotência (opcional)"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v2/appointments",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["appointments"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "useEventDriven",
                  "value": "true",
                  "description": "Ativa fluxo 4.0"
                }
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"patientId\": \"{{patientId}}\",\n  \"doctorId\": \"{{doctorId}}\",\n  \"date\": \"2025-04-15\",\n  \"time\": \"10:00\",\n  \"specialty\": \"fonoaudiologia\",\n  \"serviceType\": \"individual_session\",\n  \"billingType\": \"particular\",\n  \"paymentMethod\": \"pix\",\n  \"amount\": 200,\n  \"notes\": \"Teste particular via 4.0\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "## Evento Disparado\n- **REQUESTED**: `APPOINTMENT_CREATE_REQUESTED`\n- **RESULTADO**: `APPOINTMENT_CREATED`\n\n## Estados\n```\nprocessing_create → scheduled\n```\n\n## Response 202 Accepted\nRetorna imediatamente com status de processamento. Faça polling em Check Status."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Package (com reaproveitamento)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Correlation-Id",
                "value": "{{$guid}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v2/appointments",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["appointments"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "useEventDriven",
                  "value": "true"
                }
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"patientId\": \"{{patientId}}\",\n  \"doctorId\": \"{{doctorId}}\",\n  \"packageId\": \"{{packageId}}\",\n  \"date\": \"2025-04-15\",\n  \"time\": \"14:00\",\n  \"specialty\": \"fonoaudiologia\",\n  \"serviceType\": \"package_session\",\n  \"billingType\": \"particular\",\n  \"paymentMethod\": \"package\",\n  \"amount\": 0,\n  \"notes\": \"Teste pacote - deve reaproveitar crédito se existir\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Cria sessão de pacote com reaproveitamento automático de crédito cancelado"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Complete (Particular/Pacote)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Correlation-Id",
                "value": "{{correlationId}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Idempotency-Key",
                "value": "{{appointmentId}}_complete_normal",
                "description": "Idempotência: mesma key não duplica"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v2/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/complete",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["appointments", "{{appointmentId}}", "complete"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "useEventDriven",
                  "value": "true"
                }
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"addToBalance\": false\n}"
            },
            "description": "## Evento Disparado\n- **REQUESTED**: `APPOINTMENT_COMPLETE_REQUESTED`\n- **RESULTADO**: `APPOINTMENT_COMPLETED`\n\n## Estados\n```\nprocessing_complete → confirmed + completed\n```\n\n## Cenários\n- **Particular**: Cria Payment\n- **Pacote**: Consome sessionsDone++\n- **Per-Session**: Atualiza Package.totalPaid\n- **Convênio**: Consome guia\n- **Liminar**: Reconhece receita"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Complete (Fiado - Add to Balance)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Idempotency-Key",
                "value": "{{appointmentId}}_complete_balance"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v2/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/complete",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["appointments", "{{appointmentId}}", "complete"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "useEventDriven",
                  "value": "true"
                }
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"addToBalance\": true,\n  \"balanceAmount\": 200,\n  \"balanceDescription\": \"Sessão 15/04 - pagamento pendente\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "## Evento Disparado\n- **REQUESTED**: `APPOINTMENT_COMPLETE_REQUESTED` + `BALANCE_UPDATE_REQUESTED`\n\n## Estados\n```\nprocessing_complete → confirmed + completed (isPaid: false)\n```\n\nAdiciona ao saldo devedor do paciente (atomic $inc)"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Cancel",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Correlation-Id",
                "value": "{{correlationId}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-Idempotency-Key",
                "value": "{{appointmentId}}_cancel"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v2/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/cancel",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["appointments", "{{appointmentId}}", "cancel"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "useEventDriven",
                  "value": "true"
                }
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"reason\": \"Paciente solicitou cancelamento\",\n  \"confirmedAbsence\": false\n}"
            },
            "description": "## Evento Disparado\n- **REQUESTED**: `APPOINTMENT_CANCEL_REQUESTED`\n- **RESULTADO**: `APPOINTMENT_CANCELED`\n\n## Estados\n```\nprocessing_cancel → canceled\n```\n\n## Preservação\nSe sessão estava paga, preserva em `original*` para reaproveitamento futuro.\n\n## Regra Importante\nNÃO decrementa `sessionsDone` do pacote (igual legado)"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Check Status (Polling)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v2/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/status",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["appointments", "{{appointmentId}}", "status"]
            },
            "description": "Consulta status para polling no fluxo async.\n\n## Estados de Processamento (intermediários)\n- `processing_create` - Criando\n- `processing_cancel` - Cancelando\n- `processing_complete` - Completando\n\n## Estados Finais\n- `scheduled` - Agendado\n- `canceled` - Cancelado\n- `confirmed` + `completed` - Completado\n\n## Exemplo de Polling\n```javascript\nwhile (response.isProcessing) {\n  await sleep(2000);\n  response = await checkStatus();\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "List with Filters",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/appointments?patientId={{patientId}}&startDate=2025-04-01&endDate=2025-04-30",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["appointments"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "patientId",
                  "value": "{{patientId}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "startDate",
                  "value": "2025-04-01"
                },
                {
                  "key": "endDate",
                  "value": "2025-04-30"
                }
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "description": "Endpoints de agendamento no fluxo 4.0 com Event-Driven"
    },
    {
      "name": "🔧 Debug & Monitor",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Appointment Full (Verificação)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v2/appointments/{{appointmentId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["v2", "appointments", "{{appointmentId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Retorna agendamento completo igual ao legado (Appointment + Session + Payment populados). Use para verificar se o worker criou tudo corretamente após o 202 Accepted."
          },
          "response": []
        },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Session Details",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["sessions", "{{sessionId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Busca detalhes da sessão.\n\nCampos importantes:\n- `originalPartialAmount` - Valor preservado se cancelado\n- `originalIsPaid` - Status preservado\n- `sessionConsumed` - Se consumiu do pacote\n- `guideConsumed` - Se consumiu guia de convênio"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Payment Details",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/payments/{{paymentId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["payments", "{{paymentId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Busca detalhes do pagamento.\n\nCampos importantes:\n- `kind` - package_receipt, session_payment, revenue_recognition\n- `paymentOrigin` - auto_per_session, package_prepaid, convenio, liminar\n- `correlationId` - Para rastreamento"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Patient Balance",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/patients/{{patientId}}/balance",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["patients", "{{patientId}}", "balance"]
            },
            "description": "Consulta saldo devedor do paciente (usado no fluxo addToBalance)"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🛠️ Admin (DLQ)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Reprocessar Evento (DLQ)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/events/retry",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["admin", "events", "retry"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"eventId\": \"APPOINTMENT_CANCEL_REQUESTED_1712345678_abc123\",\n  \"queue\": \"cancel-orchestrator\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Reprocessa um evento que falhou e foi para DLQ.\n\nA idempotência garante que reprocessar não duplique."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
